```
&lt;exclusion&gt;
	&lt;artifactId&gt;jackson-dataformat-xml&lt;/artifactId&gt;				 
    &lt;groupId&gt;com.fasterxml.jackson.dataformat&lt;/groupId&gt;
&lt;/exclusion&gt;
```
The thread mentions that the dependency has been made optional, but I couldn&#39;t find the version in which that happened. 


  [1]: https://github.com/Azure/azure-service-bus-java/issues/416

